<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Taxi Express</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; color: #1e293b; }
    header { background: #0f172a; color: white; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .hero { background: #facc15; padding: 80px 20px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 10px; }
    .btn-dark { background: #0f172a; color: white; }
    .btn-light { background: white; color: #0f172a; }
    .section { padding: 70px 20px; }
    .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 18px; padding: 20px; }
    .price-box { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 18px; overflow: hidden; }
    .price-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 15px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    .price-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    footer { background: #0f172a; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Taxi Express</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Spoľahlivý odvoz 24/7</h2>
      <p>Rýchly odvoz po meste, letiskové transfery a profesionálny servis za férové ceny.</p>
      <a href="tel:+421900123456" class="btn btn-dark">Zavolať taxi</a>
      <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-light">Rezervácia</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Naše služby</h2>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card"><h3>Mestská doprava</h3><p>Rýchly odvoz po meste nonstop.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Letiskové transfery</h3><p>Presné transfery na letisko aj späť.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Firemní klienti</h3><p>VIP servis a fakturácia pre firmy.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:#f8fafc;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Cenník</h2>
      <div class="price-box">
        <div class="price-row"><span>Nástupná sadzba</span><strong>2,50 €</strong></div>
        <div class="price-row"><span>Cena za km</span><strong>0,90 €</strong></div>
        <div class="price-row"><span>Čakanie / min</span><strong>0,20 €</strong></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="kontakt" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Kontakt</h2>
      <p>📞 +421 900 123 456</p>
      <p>✉️ info@taxiexpress.sk</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Taxi Express — všetky práva vyhradené
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
